BBC Scotland will broadcast live television coverage of the Scottish League Cup quarter-final between Rangers and St Johnstone on Tuesday 28 October. BBC to screen Rangers cup quarter-final against St Johnstone  BBC Scotland will broadcast live television coverage of the Scottish League Cup quarter-final between Rangers and St Johnstone on Tuesday 28 October. 
 Rangers progressed to the quarter-finals after a 3-1 win against Falkirk. 
 Scottish Cup holders St Johnstone overcame fellow-Premiership side Kilmarnock 1-0 to progress. 
 The match at Ibrox will be screened on BBC One Scotland and streamed online with a 1915 BST kick-off. 
 